(7,2025,3721883,1758742,2376266,336945,336945,200655,102861,14953,null,null,null,21256,83,null,null,null,5.1,0.57,17.07,6.29,null,null,null,null,1374,55,'https://ahli.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/English-Annual-Report-2025.pdf','annual_report','JOD','Founded 1955 — oldest bank in East Jordan. Assets JOD 3.72B (+5.6%). Net profit JOD 21.3M (+19.4%). Deposits JOD 2.38B. Equity JOD 337M. ROE 5.1%. ROA 0.57%. CAR 17.07%. NPL 6.29% (highest ratio in sector). EPS 83 fils. 1,374 employees. 55+ branches Jordan + Palestine + Cyprus. Launched Qawn social payment app 2025 (Jordan first). New Platinum LEED HQ campus Q4 2025. Best Banking Website Jordan (Global Brand Awards 2025). CEO: Ahmed Al-Hussein. Chairman: Saad Mouasher. Shareholders: Mouasher family 20%, Byblos Bank 14.9%, SSC 11%. Subsidiaries: financial leasing + microfinance. Auditor: EY.','2026-06-15T00:45:02.575292+00:00','2026-06-15T05:51:23.295777+00:00'),
