(5,'2026-03-01',1,null,10,null,null,null,1,0.25,5,10,2,null,0,50,100,null,null,1,1,60,80,120,null,null,null,'JOD','https://websitev3-cms-cdn.bankaletihad.com/2026/03/Fees-and-Charges-Manual-English_83.pdf','Credit card late payment fee JOD 10. Over-limit fee JOD 10. Cash advance monthly rate 1.50%. Signature card annual JOD 150. Infinite (JOD) annual JOD 250. ATM cash withdrawal via JONET JOD 1. Returned cheque JOD 20.','2026-06-14T20:05:46.958526+00:00','2026-06-15T13:17:28.801715+00:00'),
(14,'2025-11-03',2,null,10,0.25,null,70,1,0.25,4,10,2,null,15,30,60,null,10,1,1,50,100,200,null,null,null,'JOD','https://www.bank-abc.com/en/CountrySites/Jordan/Products/Retail-Banking/Documents/Tariffs%20and%20charges%20English%20Version.pdf','LC issuance: max 2% min 1% annual min JOD 75. Standby LC: 2%-4% annual min JOD 100. Outgoing remittance <= JOD 500: JOD 6. JOD 500-5000: JOD 10. > JOD 5000: 0.25% max JOD 70. Same-day value adds JOD 10. RTGS local: JOD 8 branch / JOD 5 e-channels (<=ACH limit). ACH <= JOD 1000: JOD 2 branch. Inward foreign OUR: USD 30. CLIQ corporate outgoing: JOD 0.10-5.00 tiered by amount.','2026-06-14T20:05:46.958526+00:00','2026-06-15T13:17:28.801715+00:00'),
(10,'2026-05-24',2,'fixed',5,null,null,null,1,0.25,5,10,2,null,15,30,60,null,10,1,1,100,200,300,true,1,null,'JOD','https://www.safwabank.com/en/fees-and-commissions/','Islamic bank (Sharia-compliant). Returned cheque JOD 20. Certified cheque JOD 5. Chequebook 25 pages JOD 7, 50 pages JOD 10. Signature authentication JOD 2. Clearance certificate JOD 5. Standing orders own accounts: free; same bank other account: JOD 1. Salary transfer: JOD 1/month max per employer.','2026-06-14T20:05:46.958526+00:00','2026-06-15T13:00:56.444604+00:00'),
(11,'2026-03-01',2,'fixed',5,null,null,null,1,0.25,4,10,2,null,15,30,60,null,10,1,1,50,100,200,null,null,null,'JOD','https://iiabank.com.jo/sites/default/files/IIAB_Fees%20%26%20Commissions2_03-2026.2.pdf','Arabic-only PDF. CliQ+ cross-border transfer fee: JOD 2. Subsidiary of Arab Bank. Separate PDFs available for real estate finance rates (lands, buildings, building materials, istisna), auto financing, and murabaha profit rates for 2026. All PDFs Arabic only. English extraction pending.','2026-06-14T20:05:46.958526+00:00','2026-06-15T13:17:28.801715+00:00'),
(15,'2026-02-24',2,null,10,0.25,null,70,1,0.25,3,10,2,null,15,30,60,null,10,1,1,75,120,150,null,null,null,'JOD','https://www.jcbank.com.jo/uploads/2026/02/jcb260224commission-and-feesenglish.pdf','Returned cheque JOD 20. Post-dated cheque deposit JOD 1. Chequebook 25 cheques JOD 5, 40 cheques JOD 7. Safe box X-Large JOD 250. Automated safe boxes: X-Small JOD 200, Small JOD 300, Medium JOD 400, Large JOD 500, X-Large JOD 700. Corporate account management JOD 1.5/month. Company under establishment JOD 100. Currency exchange 0.5%.','2026-06-14T20:05:46.958526+00:00','2026-06-15T13:00:56.444604+00:00'),
(9,'2026-03-01',1,null,6,0.25,null,70,1,0.25,4,10,2,null,15,30,60,null,10,1,1,50,100,200,null,null,null,'JOD','https://www.jordanislamicbank.com/uploads/2026/03/salaryar.pdf','Arabic PDF. Islamic bank. Chequebook: 10 pages JOD 4 (JD), 20 pages JOD 5, 40 pages JOD 8; foreign currency: 10 pages JOD 3, 20 pages JOD 5, 40 pages JOD 7.5. Statement JOD 0.25/page. International outgoing <= JOD 500: JOD 6; JOD 500-5000: JOD 10; > JOD 5000: 0.25% max JOD 70. Guarantees: 1%-2% annual min JOD 25 (local). LC issuance: 0.375%-0.5% quarterly min JOD 40. Inward transfer <= JOD 1000: JOD 3; JOD 1000-5000: JOD 5; > JOD 5000: JOD 7.','2026-06-14T20:05:46.958526+00:00','2026-06-15T13:17:28.801715+00:00'),
